{"tid":1536184,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵（66）唔使理其他股東？政府大股東大晒？","createTime":"2019-09-03T14:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T00:18:37.000Z","uid":91918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"319138d73a2ebebc705334d17867778eb914507d","tid":1536184,"uid":91918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"啱啱過咗agm 冇耐，有冇可能要求佢開特別股東大會？質詢下嚟緊生意點做？<br />\n<br />\n雖然政府係大股東，但其他股東就唔使理？咁不如政府私有化啦！<br />\n<br />\n警察咁樣破壞港鐵點賠？<br />\n話停站就停站，點賺盡每一程？<br />\n公關做得咁差，啲人罷搭咪賺少咗？<br />\n加粉紅人睇閘成本咪高咗？<br />\n唔公開831太子站cctv點叫乘客以後放心搭？<br />\n郁下就停站，邊個仲敢買港鐵上蓋樓？<br />\n買咗全月通個啲點賠？<br />\n<br />\n支持一人買一股入場質詢！！<br />\n<br />\n（求財經台巴打賜教）<br />\n<br />\n利申：屋企人由ipo揸到依家，忠實股東。"},{"pid":"1fe8b6767268509ed69598ea9f8a353cba02f02e","tid":1536184,"uid":91918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"要求港鐵開egm交待！！"},{"pid":"d5f5a5a4f99ec3e439d7ddd0f840b88b6cb4d8af","tid":1536184,"uid":91918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:58:50.000Z","msg":"要求港鐵開egm交待！！"},{"pid":"94a0c9c6007a8319c4cae70e76e97fd02531a90d","tid":1536184,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">收野阿喂～香港自由之書又出黎收野喇，入黎睇下今次收咩</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535646/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535646/page/1</a><br />\n <br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n <br />\n國難五金專訪 [國難老闆同一眾員工已保釋,開鋪事直請留意國難五金FB]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n <br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n <br />\nFB